               <msContents>
                  <summary>Images 4r-6r: Prayer to Jesus Christ, “I Prostrate to Your Divinity” እሰግድ ለመለኮትከ, arranged for the days of the week. Images 6r-69r: Thirty-Two Miracles of Jesus Christ. Images 69r-70l: Three Miracles of the Trinity. Images 70r-76r: Introduction to the Miracles of Mary. Images 76r-79l: Three Miracles of Mary, incomplete at the end, with illuminations painted over text.  Image 6r mentions the owner, ወለተ ማርያም, in purple ink. Similarly, a list of names, male and female, appears on image 10l, written in pink ink. Illuminations are added recently over the top of text. </summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <textLang/>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
